## Accessibility

- Maintain high contrast ratios (WCAG AA minimum)
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Provide focus states (all interactive elements have focus rings)
- Include aria labels for icon-only buttons
- Test keyboard navigation

## Brand Voice

### Color Meanings (use these contextually)
- **Green:** Growth, alignment, "above the Green Line", success
- **Teal:** Clarity, flow, calm energy, information
- **Purple:** Premium, AI features, mystical, transformation
- **Yellow:** Celebration, wins, actualization, energy
- **Red:** Contrast, "below Green Line", alerts (not failure, but awareness)

### Terminology
- Use "Above the Green Line" for aligned/success states
- Use "Below the Green Line" for contrast/awareness moments
- Say "Actualize" not "Complete" or "Finish"
- Say "Vision" not "Goal" or "Plan"
- Say "Alignment" not "Progress"

